Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:20.64,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we should get started, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:24.33,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!  Since when were you part of "us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:26.10,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Ha!  What sort of question is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:28.92,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to stand in for the uselessness that is yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:31.08,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear pitifully, just like toilet paper! {toilet paper no youni mijime ni kiero} {ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:32.05,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:34.30,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:36.14,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade's working hard outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:40.06,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get in touch with everyone in the Battlefront now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.25,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,What?  What's wrong, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:54.70,AB!_Sekine,Sek,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:58.23,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing your story, it just made sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:01:00.44,AB!_Irie,Iri,0000,0000,0000,,It helped us decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:02.20,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,We're a group of people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:05.25,AB!_Irie,Iri,0000,0000,0000,,We kind of already knew it without you having to tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.85,AB!_Irie,Iri,0000,0000,0000,,After all, our vocalists are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:11.18,AB!_Sekine,Sek,0000,0000,0000,,There are no replacements for Iwasawa-san and Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:14.84,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, {\i1}she{\i0} was a horrible vocalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:19.60,AB!_Irie,Iri,0000,0000,0000,,Every day was like a culture festival.  It was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:23.35,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,Although, this is going to be difficult for people who aren't like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:24.58,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:32.02,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to start this, then finish it.\NOtherwise, it'll seem like you tricked us into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:36.78,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,If this long-lasting Battlefront's going to be disbanded,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:41.58,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,then this world has fulfilled its role, you included.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:45.08,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing that, I can believe this was for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:57.47,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just say that for a time we enjoyed the days of youth we'd missed, and that'll be enough for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:02:00.76,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.  I don't know how it'll end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:03.01,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.77,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,But well, I've quit worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:09.69,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get going now.  Just wanted to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.56,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,See you later,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:12.61,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,Newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:16.15,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be a band next time, too!  {Tsugi mo band yaruyo}{ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.99,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  I'm sure I'll enjoy it all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:20.91,AB!_Hisako,His,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:27.20,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hard work in sending off the minions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:29.67,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the worst sort of personality, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:33.84,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,I do not!  You would dare say that to God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.30,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being idiots and let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:44.85,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.20,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:48.77,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Where did all the NPCs go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.40,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,It seems these are all that's left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:55.63,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they know what we're trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:08.29,AB!_Noda,Nod,0000,0000,0000,,Scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.23,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Noda?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.71,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Nice going, Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:14.51,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean you'll fight with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.34,AB!_Noda,Nod,0000,0000,0000,,Dream on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:20.09,AB!_Noda,Nod,0000,0000,0000,,I only move when it helps Yurippe! {Ore ga ugoku no ha Yurippe no tasuke ni naru toki dakeda!} {ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:23.17,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:26.10,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a stoic guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:31.69,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Ooyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:37.86,AB!_Ooyama,Ooy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any special traits, but I thought even God would be surprised at this! {Kami-sama for bikkiru gyouten kanatte}{ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:41.99,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, show Him what you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:48.33,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go forgettin' me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:51.79,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone'd notice even if you disappeared right now! {Kono mama inaku nattemo, daremo kidukanasou dakarana!} {ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.42,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.67,AB!_T.K.,TK,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:02.34,AB!_T.K.,TK,0000,0000,0000,,Knockin' on heaven's door. {ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.54,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,That's Bob Dylan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:07.06,AB!_Noda,Nod,0000,0000,0000,,But very appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:08.08,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,What's it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:08.72,AB!_Ooyama,Ooy,0000,0000,0000,,No clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:11.28,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,The main cast's starting to get together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:21.15,AB!_Matsushita,Mat,0000,0000,0000,,What is this world?{Nanda kono sekai ha?}{ep11}  Just what is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.78,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,More like, what happened to {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:24.91,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:30.04,AB!_Matsushita,Mat,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was in the mountains for a while, but there wasn't enough food to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.50,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you... Matsushita Fifth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.71,AB!_T.K.,TK,0000,0000,0000,,Tasty candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.42,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost so much weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:37.96,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.84,AB!_Matsushita,Mat,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!  In fact, I feel better than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:44.80,AB!_Matsushita,Mat,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I might be able to take on a hundred people now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.85,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,That's actually something you do in karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:49.61,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it's a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:51.88,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,We've got all of them to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:57.02,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all get outta this world safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:57.73,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.56,AB!_T.K.,TK,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, wild heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.03,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:03.11,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to break through! {toppa suruzo!} {ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:11.99,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,The Guild is a great place to hide, but... it's enemy territory, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.29,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}our{\i0} hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:22.92,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.13,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like party time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.45,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,This is endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.84,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-san, please look below us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.81,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,There's more and more of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:37.81,AB!_Fujimaki,Fuj,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:43.28,AB!_Shiina,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.69,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:48.78,AB!_Shiina,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred...  consider that the strength of my support. {Hyakunin...  Senryoku ga fueta to omoe}{ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.13,AB!_Shiina,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.49,AB!_Shiina,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I will carry out your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.08,AB!_Shiina,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.25,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.33,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I'll leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.83,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:01.63,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.17,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Otonashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:12.14,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,More of them are coming out, so does that mean I'm heading the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.81,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:18.14,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get through that many with a handgun, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:21.94,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:23.73,AB!_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.11,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Cha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.40,AB!_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone at the Guild heard the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:32.12,AB!_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,They're all heading to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:35.62,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.12,AB!_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.88,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:46.13,AB!_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,So the war's... going to end... {Tatakai ga owaru noka...}{ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.34,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:50.19,AB!_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.26,AB!_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're disbanding, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:57.64,AB!_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,We worked hard because you guys fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.70,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the support.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.15,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Without you, none of it would have been possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:07.98,AB!_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:10.90,AB!_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:16.66,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.59,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I must have come too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.64,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,A moment's respite, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.06,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Tenshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:50.15,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I wonder if Kanade-chan's fighting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:54.14,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could have understood this world sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:58.54,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,If I had, maybe I could have been friends with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.75,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're both girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:07.88,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,This world isn't really made for it, but maybe I could have had the chance to coordinate some cute clothes with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:10.71,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,But... I guess that wasn't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:15.39,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive God, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:16.79,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:22.98,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:25.14,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost! {Kiero!} {ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.54,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:32.07,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!  Get lost!  Get lost!  Get lost!  Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:51.80,AB!_Anon,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,So you see, this equation equals this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.38,AB!_Anon,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to erase this now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:51.80,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wasn't I just thinking about something...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:58.50,AB!_Anon,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nakamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.78,AB!_Anon,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Can I erase it or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:02.52,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.27,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.02,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,That was embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.78,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.74,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing in the middle of class like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.74,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.28,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:25.58,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,"Thinking"?  So much that you stopped listening to class?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:27.11,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.11,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:30.75,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,That's stupid.  I'd love to, but that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:35.17,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,I think Fujiwara-kun is interested in you, though~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:39.80,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening to me, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.64,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Fujiwara-kun is alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.56,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara-ku-!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.52,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.10,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:51.27,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  It's me, Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.78,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, right.  Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.45,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, is something wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.16,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.87,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.79,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,You're about to say it's because of my heartache, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.70,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.16,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Get back to your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:06.79,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:11.54,AB!_Anon,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:15.80,AB!_Anon,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamura, where are you looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.72,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:22.87,AB!_Anon,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, Nakamura, start reading from the beginning of the next page.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:28.80,AB!_Anon,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:33.01,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very happy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.79,AB!_Anon,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.56,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very happy situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:40.99,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dazzling for someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.02,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,This is the kind of life everyone lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:47.58,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,So wonderful, isn't it?  I'm envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:51.58,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm obliterated from this place... can I redo my life? {ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:57.55,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to accept this ordinary happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:00.63,AB!_Anon,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.26,AB!_Hisako,Hit,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:04.35,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Losing all my memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:06.73,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,My personality would change...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.85,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I could accept it then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:12.98,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,But then, what does it mean to be reborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:15.38,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be my life anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.86,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,It would be someone else's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:22.03,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one life for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:23.78,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,And it's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:26.35,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.23,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,This is my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:31.03,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give it to anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.29,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get another, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:41.17,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I can't force it upon another, forget about it, erase it,\N trample it, laugh about it, or overdramatize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:42.43,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:48.64,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to accept the one and only life we're given, no matter how cruel and heartless it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.27,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what I mean, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.94,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.77,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I {\i1}continue{\i0} to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.48,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.32,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I can never accept another life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.05,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your hand! {te wo nobase!} {ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:21.38,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there!  Looks like we made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:25.21,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-kun and Hinata-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:27.14,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here, too, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:31.39,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I made it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:37.74,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade heard you, or rather, said she felt an explosion of your presence, and brought us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.83,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.40,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  Looks like I owe you all one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:47.16,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,You guys saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:50.81,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,But, why are you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.87,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,We left the surface to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.50,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,They said they would carry out our will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.54,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,And so you came to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.86,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,We came to fight beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:03.31,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Same difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:07.64,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.  But you make us worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.97,AB!_Angel,Ten,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you fix yourself up first?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.92,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's head out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.11,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:24.57,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Man, she never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:35.08,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, doesn't it look like they're protecting that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.92,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.  That was my thought, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:42.13,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll never get through there unless we bomb the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.71,AB!_Angel,Ten,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:46.42,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.01,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.  That's suicidal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:53.81,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:01.53,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.86,AB!_Naoi,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,Is her combat ability equivalent to that of a bomber?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.33,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.45,AB!_Hinata,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, more of them are coming already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.50,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, you go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.16,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.63,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,All right.  Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.38,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you can count on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:36.31,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,They're totally making fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:39.29,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,But this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:52.16,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many did they steal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:14:59.63,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,There's the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:01.71,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you made it this far. {Yoku tadori tsuke mashita ne}{ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:07.76,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with me.  You even have a plate on the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.84,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This place is a school, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:13.72,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,You have a unique sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:17.22,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.  That's a rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:20.73,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,A rule set by God?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.98,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,"God."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:26.15,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Highly debatable if He exists or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.36,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Very interesting, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:31.86,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have the capability to pursue that answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:34.13,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I only follow the set rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:37.39,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,So you're programmed to do this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.99,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How insightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:40.75,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you working for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:43.54,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What would be the point in giving you the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.00,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They have been here since long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:48.50,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Player...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.26,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is this software?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:57.22,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, it is software that allows one to create and alter materials in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.31,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,How is it able to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:03.02,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder myself.  I am not the developer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:07.02,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But you all create weapons from dirt, yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.07,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is that not the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:14.45,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, we're playing by the same rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:19.79,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Did the developer of the software want to become God?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.04,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder, myself.  I would not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:25.53,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're short on time, so let's get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:30.05,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What was the trigger programmed into you to start all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.30,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I am not aware of the nature of the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.09,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me rephrase the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.47,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What changed about this world, in your perspective?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:42.43,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Love has developed in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.27,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What?  "Love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:51.53,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, love.  That which is not meant to exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:58.78,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.  If love develops in this world,\Nthe two involved should be obliterated instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:02.54,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,But if it were to develop and be sustained, what would happen to this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:07.79,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If love develops, this world changes into an eternal Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:11.34,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But this world must not become that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:15.67,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That is because this is a place from which everyone must graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:17.93,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that's what someone thought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:23.35,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,However, there are times when people with amnesia wander in here after having a full life,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.60,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,having lived for people other than themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.81,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Glitches like this occur when people like that arrive here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:33.90,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,And the programmer of Angel Player was one such person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:37.07,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.  You are absolutely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:41.58,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,That same programmer found that glitch in this world and made a patch for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:44.20,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what's changing people into NPCs by using the Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.04,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:46.96,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:52.59,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,So you're telling me some NPCs were once like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:55.21,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there is another.  Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.22,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I pity the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.34,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's the programmer himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:06.93,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He continued to wait for the other one who had left this world after learning what love is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:10.48,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What?  There'd be no way for him to meet the other one again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:15.23,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The chance is astronomically small, but it isn't zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:21.91,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But the time spent waiting was too great, and he couldn't maintain his sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:25.87,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he made a program to turn himself into an NPC.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:29.71,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't that possibly have been the original intention for the Shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:33.29,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,The programmer also applied those to the world itself, so the same thing wouldn't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:35.71,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:39.42,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,So will the day ever come when they're rewarded for their actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:40.26,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.26,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a clue what's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:46.64,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what is right, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:53.27,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But since you have made it this far,\Nyou may be able to discover the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.52,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:19:00.89,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You can change the world based on your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:02.65,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:06.41,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You can choose a path that person did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:10.54,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying... I can become God?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.54,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's a different way of saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:15.79,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I can make this place into an eternal Eden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:20.34,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That person refused that conclusion, but I would not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:24.30,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,More accurately, I do not have the capacity for denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:28.64,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,God?  I can become the god of this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:38.19,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.78,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I've made this world mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.57,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.58,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This{\i0} is what I've been fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:50.00,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I could even beat Tenshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.33,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,With all of these systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:54.00,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I'm invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.84,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.89,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that to Kanade-chan anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:12.56,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Because I...  I came this far because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:14.44,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:18.44,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I sense love from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.48,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt one this strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:23.74,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's growing at an incredible rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:27.66,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:33.41,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,I came this far because I want to protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:36.92,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so you were the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:40.05,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, what do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:43.20,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Shut down every machine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.55,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.55,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:48.09,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Have you considered the consequences?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:50.06,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There is plenty of time remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.27,AB!_PlotDevice,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All eternity, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:55.69,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,You know what?  I'll tell you something valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:21:02.07,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0000,,Humans won't... even wait... for ten minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:43.23,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}It's finally... over...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.99,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}I'm sure everyone's been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:51.87,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}They should have been able to leave this place safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:56.79,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}Still, how careless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:03.38,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}I cared for everyone here as though they were my siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:10.26,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}I wanted to be like a big sister that cared for you all, so that you could be proud of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:15.17,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:17.35,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}What's become of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:22.27,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}The force that was driving me forward is dissipating.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:26.88,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}If it dissipates, I won't be able to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:38.41,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}The world took away your lives just like that, yet every moment I spent with the people here was a treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:44.17,AB!_Yuri,Yur,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}I'm starting to want to follow them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:50.97,AB!_Yuri,Red,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}Thanks.  That's enough now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:54.30,AB!_Cha,Black,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}You don't have to suffer alone, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.91,0:22:58.17,AB!_Hisako,Brown,0000,0000,0076,,{\an8}Take a rest from your long fight, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.01,0:24:21.18,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I was able to spend time with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.43,0:24:23.81,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:27.81,AB!_Otonashi,Oto,0000,0000,0000,,Graduation class speaker, Otonashi Yuzuru!
